# FitTwin — Gym Coaching & 3D Avatar Platform

## Project Overview
FitTwin is an interactive gym website where users can:
- Select specialized coaches
- Create personalized workout and nutrition plans
- Visualize their progress with a 3D avatar
- Track achievements, logs, and challenges

